In nature we can find yellow in sand, leaves and flowers, among others. In this video, CGTN Nature presents the beauty of yellow sand. Check it out! The Colors of Nature This series combines music, color and natural scenery to give viewers a sensory experience. For more: Snowy Kanas in NW China's Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)